Dreamers are active members of our communities and deserve protection from intimidation, arrest, and deportation by immigration enforcement.

@DHSgov must follow the law and uphold the rights of all DACA holders.

https://t.co/muTL7y9NKH

I am glad to see President Trump reverse the Pentagon's reckless decision to withhold crucial military aid from Ukraine.

@SecDef and @USDPColby's incompetent decision - seemingly made without the White House's knowledge and motivated by exaggerated claims of endangered U.S. military readiness - led to the death of innocent Ukrainians from Russia's airstrikes and undermined U.S. efforts to bring Putin to the negotiating table.

Achieving "peace through strength," as President Trump desires, requires the U.S. to remain steadfast in our support of Ukraine's fight against Putin's unjustified war.
